AUDE.md\",\"old_string\":\"## Lessons Learned\",\"ne‚Ä¶","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:37:29.164Z","title":"Edit","type":"file_edit"},"obs_mqwsvvu6_818c77465878":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwsvvu6_818c77465878","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01W8mUp7pkbr28fkjiXHPQwf\"} | The file /Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/CLAUDE.md has been updated successfully. (file state is current in your context ‚Äî no need to Read it back)","sessionId":"6c35a5fd-da10-4150-b228-cbb30c73ea0e","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01W8mUp7pkbr28fkjiXHPQwf\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:37:35.413Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwsvvu6_89b2d763c98f":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwsvvu6_89b2d763c98f","importance":5,"narrative":"","sessionId":"6c35a5fd-da10-4150-b228-cbb30c73ea0e","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:37:40.017Z","title":"stop","type":"other"},"obs_mqwsvvu6_464b2c14bc19":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwsvvu6_464b2c14bc19","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"command\":\"grep -n -i \\\"export\\\\|admin\\\\|client\\\" /Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/README.md | head -20\",\"description\":\"Check README for admin/export mentions\"}","sessionId":"6c35a5fd-da10-4150-b228-cbb30c73ea0e","subtitle":"{\"command\":\"grep -n -i \\\"export\\\\|admin\\\\|client\\\" /Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/README.md | head -20\",\"descript‚Ä¶","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:37:40.850Z","title":"Bash","type":"command_run"},"obs_mqwsvvu6_36c6cc7c7438":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwsvvu6_36c6cc7c7438","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_016X1eSB3FxW42RMfPUDBGJ2\"} | 3:> A full-stack web application for an accounting firm: premium public marketing site, encrypted client document portal, secure messaging, and an admin management panel ‚Äî all in one monorepo.\n11:1. **Public marketing site** ‚Äî A professional dark-navy we