ecurity vulnerabilities.\\n\\nREPOSITORY CONTEXT: Spring Boot 3.5 / Java 21 backend + Angular 21 frontend. Authentication via JWT cookie (httpOnly, SameSite=Strict). Admin export feature being added.\\n\\nKEY NEW FILES:\\n\\n**backend/src/main/java/com/gwhaitech/acc‚Ä¶","sessionId":"6c35a5fd-da10-4150-b228-cbb30c73ea0e","subtitle":"{\"description\":\"Security vulnerability identification\",\"prompt\":\"You are a senior security engineer. Analyze the follow‚Ä¶","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:04:24.414Z","title":"Agent","type":"subagent"},"obs_mqwtkgro_79c3dcdb0235":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgro_79c3dcdb0235","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01GzGDw6CCm1AwEPfSqPSoMg\"} | [{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Here is the complete security analysis, based on reading the actual source files.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Security Review: Admin Export Feature\\n\\n### FINDING 1 ‚Äî HIGH | Confidence: 8/10\\n**ZIP Slip: `d.getFilename()` is unsanitized in the ZIP entry path**\\n\\n**Location:** `AdminExportService.java` lines 118 and 156\\n\\n```java\\nString ‚Ä¶","sessionId":"6c35a5fd-da10-4150-b228-cbb30c73ea0e","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01GzGDw6CCm1AwEPfSqPSoMg\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:09:24.151Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkgro_82a7b07312a0":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgro_82a7b07312a0","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"description\":\"False-positive filter: ZIP slip finding\",\"prompt\":\"You are a security engineer performing false-positive filtering on a security finding.\\n\\nFINDING: ZIP Slip via unsanitized filename in ZIP entry path\\n\\nIn `AdminExportService.java`, the ZIP entry name is constructed as:\\n```java\\nString entryName = folderName + \\\"/\\\" + d.getYear() + \\\"/\\\" + d.getFilename();\\n```\\n\\n`d.getFilenam‚Ä¶","sessionId":"6c35a5fd-da10-4150-b228-cbb30c73ea0e","subtitle":"{\"description\":\"False-positive filter: ZIP slip finding\",\"prompt\":\"You are a security engineer performing false-positiv‚Ä¶","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:09:42.477Z","title":"Agent","type":"subagent"},"obs_mqwtkgro_1b1b3d1418e7":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgro_1b1b3d1418e7","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01EBJEEZd7TnpNPBnKEULZan\"} | [{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"**Confidence score: 3 ‚Äî EXCLUDE**\\n\\n**Reasoning:**\\n\\n**Attack path requires out-of-band DB write.** `FileUploadValidator.validateFilename` (line 74) blocks `/`, `\\\\`, and `..` at upload time for every file entering the system. There is no code path by which a regular portal user or external attacker can write a filename wi‚Ä¶","sessionId":"6c35a5fd-da10-4150-b228-cbb30c73ea0e","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01EBJEEZd7TnpNPBnKEULZan\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:09:59.954Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkgro_e8e96e442546":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgro_e8e96e442546","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"description\":\"False-positive filter: CSV injection finding\",\"prompt\":\"You are a security engineer performing false-positive filtering on a security finding.\\n\\nFINDING: CSV Injection via portal user email in exported CSV\\n\\nIn `AdminExportService.buildCsv()`, the CSV includes a \\\"Linked Portal User Email\\\" column. The `csvField()` method only quotes values containing `,`, `\\\"`, or `\\\\n` ‚Äî it do‚Ä¶","sessionId":"6c35a5fd-da10-4150-b228-cbb30c73ea0e","subtitle":"{\"description\":\"False-positive filter: CSV injection finding\",\"prompt\":\"You are a security engineer performing false-po‚Ä¶","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:09:51.080Z","title":"Agent","type":"subagent"},"obs_mqwtkgro_0d55a65406f1":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgro_0d55a65406f1","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01A8ZnKPN5BAChsNWfZqHECQ\"} | [{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I have all the information needed. Here is the assessment:\\n\\n---\\n\\n**VERDICT: EXCLUDE ‚Äî Confidence 4/10**\\n\\n**Reasoning:**\\n\\n**1. The `csvField()` gap is real but narrow.**\\nThe method at lines 185‚Äì191 of `AdminExportService.java` does not prefix-sanitize `=`, `+`, `-`, or `@`. This is a textbook CSV injection code patte‚Ä¶","sessionId":"6c35a5fd-da10-4150-b228-cbb30c73ea0e","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01A8ZnKPN5BAChsNWfZqHECQ\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:10:39.139Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkgro_7e95d82e29d4":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgro_7e95d82e29d4","importance":5,"narrative":"","sessionId":"6c35a5fd-da10-4150-b228-cbb30c73ea0e","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:10:56.508Z","title":"stop","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkgro_1e51c2eb3d04":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/admin-client-export/tasks.md"],"id":"obs_mqwtkgro_1e51c2eb3d04","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"replace_all\":false,\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/admin-client-export/tasks.md\",\"old_string\":\"- [ ] 3.5 Run /security-review on the branch diff; address Critical/High/Medium findings before proceeding\",\"new_string\":\"- [x] 3.5 Run /security-review on the branch diff; address Critical/High/Medium findings before proceeding (no C/H/M findings; two Low findings, ‚Ä¶","sessionId":"6c35a5fd-da10-4150-b228-cbb30c73ea0e","subtitle":"{\"replace_all\":false,\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/admin-client-export/tasks.md\",\"‚Ä¶","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:10:59.297Z","title":"Edit","type":"file_edit"},"obs_mqwtkgro_dc91504aab4b":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgro_dc91504aab4b","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01MBxV5CE6UNeDCifQwKRCjR\"} | The file /Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/openspec/changes/admin-client-export/tasks.md has been updated successfully