igration adds a NOT NULL column (e.g. `users.name`, `clients.admin_id`), raw SQL INSERT helpers in `@DataJpaTest` tests break silently at runtime ‚Äî the compiler won't catch missing columns. After any NOT NULL migration, grep `src/test` for INSERT statemen‚Ä¶","sessionId":"6c35a5fd-da10-4150-b228-cbb30c73ea0e","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01XgTQqRdbAuY1ZmpV52ojG9\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:37:15.052Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mqwtkgro_6cdb38a24cb7":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/CLAUDE.md"],"id":"obs_mqwtkgro_6cdb38a24cb7","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/CLAUDE.md\",\"offset\":180,\"limit\":5}","sessionId":"6c35a5fd-da10-4150-b228-cbb30c73ea0e","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/CLAUDE.md\",\"offset\":180,\"limit\":5}","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:37:15.028Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqwtkgro_e4107d4008a8":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":["/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/CLAUDE.md"],"id":"obs_mqwtkgro_e4107d4008a8","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/CLAUDE.md\",\"offset\":220,\"limit\":10}","sessionId":"6c35a5fd-da10-4150-b228-cbb30c73ea0e","subtitle":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/gwang/Develop/accounting-firm/CLAUDE.md\",\"offset\":220,\"limit\":10}","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:37:17.545Z","title":"Read","type":"file_read"},"obs_mqwtkgro_73d23488fae0":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mqwtkgro_73d23488fae0","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01HZACZ189tSvor4PuWher8p\"} | <system-reminder>Warning: the file exists but is shorter than the provided offset (220). The file has 206 lines.</system-reminder>","sessionId":"6c35a5fd-da10-4150-b228-cbb30c73ea0e","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"toolu_01HZACZ189tSvor4PuWher8p\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-17T21:37:17.561Z","title":"post_tool_use",